- 'get_legal_moves' to get a UCI formatted list of available moves
- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

Player_Black (to Proxy):

I’m ready to move as Black. You can choose one of these actions:

- get_current_board — see the full board layout and turn
- get_legal_moves — get all legal UCI moves from the current position
- make_move <UCI> — play a specific move (e.g., make_move e7e5)

- 'make_move <UCI formatted move>' when you are ready to complete your turn (e.g., 'make_move e2e4')

- make_move <UCI> — to make a move now (e.g., make_move e7e5)
